ain by the Normans in the form <i>Joscelin</i>. This was originally a derivative, <i>Gautzelin</i>, of the name of a Germanic tribe, the <i>Gauts</i>. The spelling of the first syllable was altered because the name was taken as a double diminutive (with the Old French suffixes <i>-el</i> and <i>-in</i>) of <i>Josce</i> (  see  Joyce  )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Joscelyn FritzReinfred was born about 1168, in Sussex, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with Joscelyn FritzReinfred."},"et":{"Abt 1168–":"umbes 1168–Surnud","1168–Male":"1168–Surnud","1194–1253":"1194–1253","1168–Female":"1168–Surnud","Abt 1168":"umbes 1168","1168":"1168","1253":"1253","1194":"1194","Of Echingham, Sussex, England":"Sussex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Sussex, England":"Sussex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1168–":"noin 1168–Kuollut","1168–Male":"1168–Kuollut","1194–1253":"1194–1253","1168–Female":"1168–Kuollut","Abt 1168":"noin 1168","1168":"1168","1253":"1253","1194":"1194","Of Echingham, Sussex, England":"Sussex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Sussex, England":"Sussex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1168–":"environ 1168–Décédée","1168–Male":"1168–Décédé","1194–1253":"1194–1253","1168–Female":"1168–Décédée","Abt 1168":"environ 1168","1168":"1168","1253":"1253","1194":"1194","Of Echingham, Sussex, England":"Sussex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Sussex, England":"Sussex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Joscelyn FritzReinfred est née environ 1168, à Sussex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Joscelyn FritzReinfred."},"de":{"Abt 1168–":"um 1168–Verstorben","1168–Male":"1168–Verstorben","1194–1253":"1194–1253","1168–Female":"1168–Verstorben","Abt 1168":"um 1168","1168":"1168","1253":"1253","1194":"1194","Of Echingham, Sussex, England":"Sussex, England, United Kingdom","Sussex, England":"Sussex, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Joscelyn FritzReinfred wurde um 1168 in Sussex, England, United Kingdom gebor